          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-4 h-4"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> Metode Tartili jilid 1–4</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600"><span class="flex-shrink-0 text-emerald-500"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-4 h-4"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> Tartil & tajwid dasar</li>
