          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-7 h-7"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Kajian Anak</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5">Kajian akhlak mulia, doa harian, fiqih anak, dan pendidikan karakter Islami yang menyenangkan.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
